dc_title_s: Adair County, Iowa, 1948, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol BJT. Form of individual image numbering: BJT-1D-[number], or BJT-2D-[number]."Flying completed Aug. 18, 1948." Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, Kentucky.
